				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repro steps:\r\n1. Start the game\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. oe readyattackonden\r\n4. Blow the horn and side wit the goblin (kill all tieflings at the gate).\r\n5. goto 175.70, 21.56, 529.96\r\n6. Kill all tieflings.\r\n7. goto 258.42, 14.76, 525.52\r\n8. Kill all druids.\r\n9. Follow the goblins to 285.38, 1.25, 470.33\r\n10. Talk with Goblin Sharp-eye\r\n "
				},
